		<div class="container container--content">
			<img class="section-token" src="img/token-about.svg" alt="">
			<h2 class="section-header">Who's Behind Radical Product?</h2>
			<p>Radical Product started as a collaboration between Radhika Dutt, Nidhi Aggarwal, and Geordie Kaytes — three Boston-area digital product leaders who have been in the trenches more than once.</p>
